data.description: If you are looking for a better than new ranch style home with main level living, this 2021 built home may be the perfect fit for you! Step inside to discover luxury vinyl plank flooring throughout the entire home. Boasting vaulted celling’s, allowing for a luxurious open concept living experience. The kitchen is a true highlight, showcasing a plethora of storage in the modern style cabinets, electric range top, and a spacious quartz kitchen island with pendent lighting, it also includes a spacious pantry for added storage! The kitchen is open to the eat in dining area and flows right into the living room, perfect for entertaining. The sliding glass door gives you ease of access to your backyard to enjoy outdoor living, backing to open space. This grand open concept floorplan is ideal for both fun gatherings, and daily living. The larger primary bedroom is a retreat featuring space for a king size bed, vaulted ceiling with a ceiling fan, and attached bathroom. The primary bathroom features double vanity sinks, a walk-in shower with sizeable bench, quartz countertops, a walk-in closet, and a door on the powder room, offering both comfort and privacy. Your secondary bathroom is situated near the front of the home and features double vanity sinks, and quartz countertops. This exquisite single-level living ranch-style home with mountain views from your front porch will not last long!
